  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will be a single subject study to evaluate the efficacy of the HER2 kinase
      inhibitor, neratinib, in a patient with metastatic bladder cancer harboring a HER2-GRB7 gene
      fusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
